survey_response.review_text: Dr Mallesh is very friendly and listens to the issues clearly. He provides maximum possible natural way of treatment unless it’s really necessary to go for medicinal options for new born baby. I like this approach. Whereas in private larger group of hospital they try to get money by providing complex treatments. However Dr. Mallesh is not that kind, he clearly assess the actual problem and provide solid solution for the same. Due to this pandemic situation he provided good video consultation whereas my baby’s umbilical cord issue is resolved now. Thanks for your support.

I liked that without any waiting time , I was able to meet doctor on time . He patiently listened to my worries and then explained me the reason and the treatment.  My daughter was very positive after visiting the paediatrician and ready to visit again. thanks Doctor.

Actually we visited Dr. Mallesh pediatrician for the bumps on the skin for my kid since its an skin related issue he first done normal consultation then sent to Dr Kavya, skin specialist... As soon she saw  bumps she identified the problem and gave proper medication, there is an improvement within 1 Day. also they both care for the patients very well they will be available on what's app any time will give immediate response. Overall experience was too good.
